          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By author*.In order to reduce the nuclear",
                "uncertainties affecting the reaction rate estimate was",
                "performed an experimental study of the 18O(p,alpha)15N",
                "reaction by means of the Trojan Horse Method(THM),",
                "which is an indirect technique to measure the relative",
                "energy-dependence of a charged-particle reaction cross",
                "section at energies well below the Coulomb barrier."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin self-supported deuterated polyethylene CD(2)",
                "targets were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "IOCH",
                "PS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The detection setup consists of a telescope, made up of",
                "an ionization chamber and a silicon position sensitive",
                "detector(PSD A) on one side with respect to the beam",
                "direction and three additional silicon PSD's(B,C and D)",
                "on the opposite side."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
